      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this peerless example of automotive excellence. Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle has been maintained with uncompromising attention to detail, ensuring an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning collector. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare to encounter. This is, without question, the finest specimen currently available on the market.",
