    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to check out this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you in the driver's seat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
