    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-ready condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, and that distinct new-car scent remains. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions flawlessly, providing a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. All service records are up to date, performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
