    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and doesn't have a single scratch on it. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this beauty is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
