    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) in pristine, concours-level condition. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear power band and razor-sharp throttle response. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise gate engagement with optimized ratios for spirited driving. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package, the chassis retains its factory-spec lateral stiffness and damping rates. Every mechanical component\u2014from the Brembo four-piston monobloc calipers to the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry\u2014operates within original tolerances. This is a mechanically flawless, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist, showing no signs of synchro wear or oil consumption.",
